text: Cesare Maniago (born January 13, 1939) is a Canadian former professional ice hockey goaltender. Maniago played the majority of his National Hockey League (NHL) career for the Minnesota North Stars. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian ice hockey goaltenders Category:Toronto Maple Leafs players Category:Montreal Canadiens players Category:New York Rangers players Category:Minnesota North Stars players Category:People from Trail, British Columbia Category:Vancouver Canucks players Category:Ice hockey people from British Columbia
